<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871214-0130 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:Applied Materials Inc.</HL><DD> 12/14/87</DD><SO>  </SO><IN> )SO WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)WNEWS AMAT </IN><DATELINE> APPLIED MATERIALS INC. (Santa Clara, Calif.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>   James W. Bagley, formerly senior vice president, operations, was named president and chief operating officer of this maker of semiconductor production equipment. As president, Mr. Bagley succeeds James C. Morgan, who remains chairman and chief executive officer. The chief operating officer post is new. Mr. Bagley was also elected a director, increasing board membership to seven. </TEXT></DOC>